@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Welcome to our anonymous chat service. This privacy policy outlines how we handle your data and ensure your privacy while using our platform.</p>

<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
<p>Our chat service allows users to engage in anonymous conversations with other users. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your interactions on our platform remain confidential and secure.</p>

<h2>2. Anonymity</h2>
<p>Users can participate in chats without disclosing any personal information. You do not need to provide any identifying details such as names, email addresses, or phone numbers. All interactions are conducted anonymously.</p>

<h2>3. Data Collection</h2>
<p>We do not collect personal data from users. The only data collected is for operational purposes, such as IP addresses, which help us manage and maintain the service. This data is not used to identify or track users beyond what is necessary for providing the service.</p>

<h2>4. Chat Message Storage</h2>
<p>Chat messages are stored temporarily to facilitate communication between users. These messages are not linked to personal identifiers and are deleted after they are no longer needed. We do not use chat messages for any purpose other than providing the chat service.</p>

<h2>5. Security</h2>
<p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect the data transmitted through our chat service. However, please note that no system can be completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute protection against unauthorized access or breaches.</p>

<h2>6. User Responsibilities</h2>
<p>While using our chat service, users are expected to comply with our terms of use and adhere to legal standards. We reserve the right to monitor and manage the chat service to ensure that it is used appropriately and to maintain a safe environment for all participants.</p>

<h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. We encourage users to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect their data.</p>

<h2>8. Contact Information</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or our chat service, please contact us through our support channels.</p>
